                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 8.035,
                                "byte_start": 28672,
                                "byte_stop": 60855,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion of the Court in Thor Power Tool against the Commissioner of Internal Revenue will be announced by Mr. Justice Blackmun."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 8.035,
                        "stop": 104.717,
                        "byte_start": 60855,
                        "byte_stop": 447572,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 15045,
                            "name": "Harry A. Blackmun",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/harry_a_blackmun",
                            "last_name": "Blackmun",
                            "roles": [
                                {
                                    "id": 2689,
                                    "type": "scotus_justice",
                                    "date_start": 13755600,
                                    "date_end": 775890000,
                                    "appointing_president": "Richard Nixon",
                                    "role_title": "Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "institution_name": "Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/preson_role\/scotus_justice\/2689"
                                }
                            ],
                            "thumbnail": {
                                "id": 32712,
                                "mime": "image\/png",
                                "size": 50281,
                                "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/sites\/default\/files\/harry_a_blackmun.png"
                            },
                            "length_of_service": 8821,
                            "identifier": "harry_a_blackmun"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 8.035,
                                "stop": 15.899,
                                "byte_start": 60855,
                                "byte_stop": 92306,
                                "text": "Well, this is a federal income tax case and it comes to us from the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 15.899,
                                "stop": 27.271,
                                "byte_start": 92306,
                                "byte_stop": 137759,
                                "text": "That Court has had the United States\u0027 Tax Court before it decided the issues in favor of the Commissioner of Internal Revenue and against the corporate taxpayer."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 27.271,
                                "stop": 29.173,
                                "byte_start": 137759,
                                "byte_stop": 145387,
                                "text": "There are two issues involved."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 29.173,
                                "stop": 38.2,
                                "byte_start": 145387,
                                "byte_stop": 181541,
                                "text": "One has to do with the amount of an addition by an accrual basis taxpayer to a reserve or bad debts."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 38.2,
                                "stop": 45.934,
                                "byte_start": 181541,
                                "byte_stop": 212470,
                                "text": "And the other concerns inventory write-downs when the taxpayer concludes that its inventory is excessive."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 45.934,
                                "stop": 59.156,
                                "byte_start": 212470,
                                "byte_stop": 265341,
                                "text": "These obviously are not issues of such public interest as to merit extended comment here but they are of definite concern to accountants and to those who administer the income tax laws."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 59.156,
                                "stop": 67.998,
                                "byte_start": 265341,
                                "byte_stop": 300763,
                                "text": "It will suffice to say that in an opinion filed today the Court unanimously affirms the judgment of the Court of Appeals."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 67.998,
                                "stop": 81.577,
                                "byte_start": 300763,
                                "byte_stop": 354994,
                                "text": "We hold that the Commissioner did not abuse his discretion when he ruled that the inventory write-down effectuated by the taxpayer did not reflect income clearly for income tax purposes."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 81.577,
                                "stop": 90.215,
                                "byte_start": 354994,
                                "byte_stop": 389580,
                                "text": "And also that he did not abuse his discretion when he disallowed in part the taxpayer\u0027s addition to its bad debt reserve."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 90.215,
                                "stop": 104.717,
                                "byte_start": 389580,
                                "byte_stop": 447572,
                                "text": "In reaching these conclusions we emphasize that what may be appropriate for accounting purposes does not necessarily govern for income tax purposes."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 104.717,
                        "stop": 107.876,
                        "byte_start": 447572,
